{"tid":1513214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員涉騙6同袍逾8.3萬元　被控欺詐周五答辯","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T05:14:46.000Z","uid":104865,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3e08d77c14f40ddb408fc44379f0adf3bcc4b4c9","tid":1513214,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:34:11.000Z","msg":"廉署落案起訴一名高級警員6項欺詐罪，涉嫌以欺詐手段，騙取6名警員合共超過83000元貸款。廉署准被告保釋，星期五在西九龍裁判法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n49歲被告林仲文，案發時在深水埗分區一個巡邏小隊工作，他在2016年認識6名同於該巡邏小隊工作的警員。<br />\n　　 <br />\n控罪指，被告涉嫌於2018年4月至5月期間，先後10次不誠實地向6名同袍訛稱需要金錢支付母親在內地的醫療費，並意圖詐騙誘使對方向他提供10筆共超過83000萬元的貸款，被告從每名警員取得的款項由大約6千元至25000元不等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警犬連自己人都呃"},{"pid":"84ef7156b5c1004bf0cf1325b07f92bbb8fc96f5","tid":1513214,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"補link: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477317-20190828.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477317-20190828.htm&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5HGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=b46f5d0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477317-20190828.htm&h=21778b21\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477317-20190828.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1a1236f84efb09de5f939d03f4510c2a22007a96","tid":1513214,"uid":22360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"乜嘢係全港最大犯罪集團"},{"pid":"cbc7386912e21a15ce02d5fb1f744198d9b37365","tid":1513214,"uid":168703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0Ypvtp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0Ypvtp.jpg&h=9c33fbd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c8a11a9c6812d2d9a6a4ed83d28c5768b457ca7","tid":1513214,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"可以係連